{"tid":1334521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郭炳聯發信感謝新城市廣場員工","createTime":"2019-07-20T06:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T06:57:54.000Z","uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"456665955f22b7a9c71ebe5187820c1f2833331d","tid":1334521,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:40:24.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】新地主席郭炳聯向全體員工發信，感謝新城市廣場員工。<br />\n郭炳聯指星期日在新城市廣場發生的警民事件，前線同事在緊急情況下努力維持秩序，管理公司啟勝的員工亦盡力澄清事件。<br />\n<br />\n郭炳聯和管理層感謝不同崗位的員工，為他們的專業和辛勞表示衷心謝意，他又指，集團尊重同事個人政治取向以及和平表達意見的自由，相信員工行使權利的同時，應避免影響工作，對員工的專業操守有絕對信心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=356032&amp;fbclid=IwAR3uHoytOf4APhi7Oei9kK_-nRKMrutMT3pqmwBDibBioST7c7UVCKehYZ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356032%26fbclid%3DIwAR3uHoytOf4APhi7Oei9kK_-nRKMrutMT3pqmwBDibBioST7c7UVCKehYZ8&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbhD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=be126907\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356032%26fbclid%3DIwAR3uHoytOf4APhi7Oei9kK_-nRKMrutMT3pqmwBDibBioST7c7UVCKehYZ8&h=0d18362f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=356032&amp;fbclid=IwAR3uHoytOf4APhi7Oei9kK_-nRKMrutMT3pqmwBDibBioST7c7UVCKehYZ8</a>"},{"pid":"8cb8f5acded25b9f7e1dd57c4523ab7f4f750e20","tid":1334521,"uid":111955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:42:15.000Z","msg":"個個唔敢返工都維持秩序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57ddc91b64f803490c29a1fab70a049b983712e","tid":1334521,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:57:54.000Z","msg":"push"}]}